        <h2>What's New in 0.5.45</h2>
        <h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Fixed plugin not appearing in Ableton Live and other DAWs on some machines</li>
          <li>Plugin now loads significantly faster during DAW scanning — heavy audio analysis is deferred until first use</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Improvements</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Simplified installer — no more destination selection screen, always installs system-wide</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="source">Build 1105 &middot; <a href="https://github.com/danielraffel/PlunderTube/commit/fd63f1e9">fd63f1e9</a> on main</p>
      ]]></description>
